{"ts":"2026-07-19T15:37:42.475Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-19T15:37:42.475Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-19T15:37:42.471Z","author":"maintainer-agent","text":"Evidence: ids.token_length settings section (default 4, bounds 4-12, validator-rejected outside range), generateItemId reads it with +6 escalation headroom, ids_token_length pm-config key (new integer max bound support), storage_integrity now reports validate_storage_duplicate_item_ids with per-id path lists + remediation hint. Manual sandbox: 6-char id minted (sbx-eum8uh), out-of-range 13 rejected, cross-folder duplicate detected as warning validate_storage_duplicate_item_ids:1. Collision math documented in MERGE_SAFETY.md. Specs: id-generation/settings-store/nested-settings/validate-command all green."}]}],"before_hash":"a4ee2ec093171924d23be2884bfc5dfc53ba4cdd64d3d7283b4b0d8ccb576cae","after_hash":"48db602dfbbd3278877bd05b00dd42743854b178fda78fd5df8cdd8d44b877e3"}
