{"ts":"2026-07-19T15:38:34.407Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"learning_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-19T15:38:34.407Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/learnings","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-19T15:38:34.402Z","author":"maintainer-agent","text":"Local idExists probes cannot prevent cross-branch id collisions — only entropy (ids.token_length) shrinks the odds and only post-merge duplicate-id detection catches the residue. Birthday math for base36 tokens at 1% collision: len4 ~184 unsynced creations, len6 ~6.6k, len8 ~238k."}]}],"before_hash":"483a36aa787446a856c8bf8577ddf02c8454fe05e5b23d2e233d7c1c75c27bb9","after_hash":"9f8eb2b38afb78663e14e80f9beced61d47ad992380ef858fffe6745332121fc"}
{"ts":"2026-07-19T16:09:08.025Z","author":"codex-wide-sdk-20260719","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-19T16:09:08.025Z","author":"codex-wide-sdk-20260719","text":"Acceptance and regression evidence: configurable id generation is exercised through create/copy/CLI registration/settings validation, with duplicate item IDs detected across type folders as a storage-integrity error. A packed-package install in a fresh temporary npm+git project configured a six-character token, created ac-e5d545, validated clean storage, then detected validate_storage_duplicate_item_ids after a cross-folder duplicate was introduced. Full suite: 317 files, 5,975 tests, 100/100/100/100 coverage."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-19T16:09:08.025Z"}],"before_hash":"9f8eb2b38afb78663e14e80f9beced61d47ad992380ef858fffe6745332121fc","after_hash":"be42f3e7577fe59f692d440a3c9cd482255e8c89c61f054ad3dccc0f1862bd51"}
